			"index": "am",
			"roundness": null,
			"seed": 849006862,
			"version": 373,
			"versionNonce": 948494085,
			"isDeleted": false,
			"boundElements": [],
			"updated": 1773773379444,
			"link": null,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "O(3N^3+2N^2+1)\nso remove constants\n\nO(N^3+N^2)\n\nso here we get complexity but this is not correct \n\nas 1million+100 , so we neglect 100 so neglect loose constrains\n\nhere N^2 is a loose constrain so out compx is\n\nO(N^3) ",
			"rawText": "O(3N^3+2N^2+1)\nso remove constants\n\nO(N^3+N^2)\n\nso here we get complexity but this is not correct \n\nas 1million+100 , so we neglect 100 so neglect loose constrains\n\nhere N^2 is a loose constrain so out compx is\n\nO(N^3) ",
			"fontSize": 16,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "O(3N^3+2N^2+1)\nso remove constants\n\nO(N^3+N^2)\n\nso here we get complexity but this is not correct \n\nas 1million+100 , so we neglect 100 so neglect loose constrains\n\nhere N^2 is a loose constrain so out compx is\n\nO(N^3) ",
			"autoResize": true,
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"hasTextLink": false
		},
